               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary><p>A multi-text (possibly a composite in fact) manuscript containing 3 <foreign xml:lang="ta">Nīti</foreign> works, the first two being 2 of the <title xml:lang="ta">Patiṉeṇkīḻkaṇakku</title>:
<list rend="numbered">
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Nāṉmaṇikkaṭikai</title> (in 101 stanzas, but incomplete as f14 = stanzas  53-56 is missing) (U2).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Tirikaṭukam</title> (in 100 stanzas, complete) (U3).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Nītineṟiviḷakkam</title> (incomplete: stanzas 1-56 only) (U4).</item>
</list></p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (December 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> 
                  </summary>
                  
